PN,31301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe prime minister has insisted he is
OL,8,Fnot lifting sanctions on Russian oil
OL,9,F"in any way whatsoever" after being
OL,10,Faccused of easing restrictions on oil
OL,11,Frefined in third-party countries.
OL,13,FSpeaking during Prime Minister's
OL,14,FQuestions on Wednesday, the PM said
OL,15,Fthe "strong new package" of sanctions
OL,16,Fannounced on Tuesday goes "well
OL,17,Fbeyond" existing measures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe government has been eager to push
OL,8,Fback on claims of easing sanctions,
OL,9,Fafter issuing a trade licence which
OL,10,Fallows for the import of jet fuel and
OL,11,Fdiesel refined in third countries amid
OL,12,Fsurging costs due to the Iran war.
OL,14,FIt has been heavily criticised by
OL,15,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch, who
OL,16,Fsaid it is "insane" to water down
OL,17,Fsanctions when the UK government is
OL,18,Frefusing to fully exploit North Sea
OL,19,Fresources.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe Labour chairwoman of the Foreign
OL,8,FAffairs Committee, Dame Emily
OL,9,FThornberry, also criticised the move,
OL,10,Ftelling BBC Radio 4's Today programme:
OL,11,F"They (Ukraine) don't understand,
OL,12,Fgiven that we promised that we would
OL,13,Fstop this loophole in October, and we
OL,14,Fstill haven't done it. In fact, it
OL,15,Fseems to have got worse. People feel
OL,16,Fvery let down."
OL,26,@sD@GpmsD@Opn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FTrade minister Sir Chris Bryant later
OL,8,Fapologised to MPs for the government's
OL,9,F"clumsy" handling of the issue and
OL,10,Fsaid he wanted the licence to be as
OL,11,F"temporary as possible".
OL,13,FHe apologised and insisted the
OL,14,Fmeasures would strengthen the
OL,15,Fsanctions regime on Russia.
OL,17,FOn Wednesday, the government banned
OL,18,Fthese imports but issued a temporary
OL,19,Ftrade license, creating an exemption
OL,20,Fto phase in the ban.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FBryant insisted the trade license
OL,8,Fissued today was a temporary
OL,9,Fexemption, and once lifted, would
OL,10,Fresult in the underlying sanctions
OL,11,Fbanning these products completely.
OL,13,FThe government pledged to close this
OL,14,Floophole, which allowed the import of
OL,15,FRussian oil products from third-party
OL,16,Fcountries in October last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FAt the time, a government press
OL,8,Frelease announced: "To further
OL,9,Frestrict the flow of funds to the
OL,10,FKremlin, the UK has today announced
OL,11,Fthat we will ban imports of oil
OL,12,Fproducts refined in third countries
OL,13,Ffrom Russian-origin crude oil.
OL,15,F"By removing Russian oil from the
OL,16,Fmarket, taking steps towards peace and
OL,17,Fin turn building a more secure Europe,
OL,18,Fwe are directly strengthening the UK's
OL,19,Fnational and energy security ` key
OL,20,Ffoundations of this government's Plan
OL,21,Ffor Change."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe trade licence, which came into
OL,8,Feffect on Wednesday, permits the
OL,9,Fimports "indefinitely", and comes amid
OL,10,Frising prices as a result of the
OL,11,Fconflict in Iran and the closure of
OL,12,Fthe Strait of Hormuz.
OL,14,FAccording to the licence, the
OL,15,Fsanctions carve-out will be
OL,16,Fperiodically reviewed as fuel prices
OL,17,Ffluctuate.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe government had previously
OL,8,Fannounced the UK would block Russian
OL,9,Foil refined in other countries in a
OL,10,Fbid to "further restrict the flow of
OL,11,Ffunds to the Kremlin".
OL,13,FEarlier this week, US Treasury
OL,14,FSecretary Scott Bessent extended a 30-
OL,15,Fday sanctions waiver allowing the
OL,16,Fpurchase of Russian oil shipments
OL,17,Falready at sea.
OL,26,@rD@HOUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"This extension will provide
OL,8,Fadditional flexibility, and we will
OL,9,Fwork with these nations to provide
OL,10,Fspecific licenses as needed," he
OL,11,Fposted on X.
OL,13,FIt comes amid new figures showing
OL,14,Fpetrol prices have eclipsed the
OL,15,Fprevious high set during the Iran oil
OL,16,Fcrisis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
