OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, the RAC said the average
OL,8,Fprice of a litre of petrol at UK
OL,9,Fforecourts stands at 158.5p, which is
OL,10,Fthe most expensive it has been since
OL,11,FDecember 2022.
OL,13,FFollowing the beginning of the
OL,14,Fconflict in the Middle East on
OL,15,FFebruary 28, the price had previously
OL,16,Fpeaked at 158.3p on April 15.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FResponding to the government's
OL,8,Fannouncement of a temporary carve-out
OL,9,Ffor third-country Russian oil
OL,10,Fproducts, Ukraine's head of sanctions
OL,11,Fpolicy, Vladyslav Vlasiuk, said he
OL,12,Funderstood why the UK had made the
OL,13,Fdecision it had, but disagreed with
OL,14,Fthe approach.
OL,16,F"Pressure on Russia should only
OL,17,Fincrease, while market stability
OL,18,Fshould be ensured by addressing root
OL,19,Fcauses ` Hormuz," Vlasiuk wrote in a
OL,20,Fpost on X.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
