OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FEarlier in the Commons, the PM
OL,13,Fannounced the abandoning of plans to
OL,14,Fincrease fuel duty from September.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
