PN,31313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FStarmer told MPs: "I can announce
OL,8,Ftoday that we are giving our hauliers
OL,9,Fa 12-month road tax holiday, helping
OL,10,Fto keep prices down."And we are
OL,11,Fbacking drivers by extending the
OL,12,Ffreeze in fuel duty for the rest of
OL,13,Fthe year."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779365472
OL,3,CUK delays sanctions on third-party
OL,4,CRussian oil as new restrictions
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe chancellor had previously
OL,8,Fannounced in her November 2025 budget
OL,9,Fthat the 5p per litre fuel duty
OL,10,Freduction ` introduced by the
OL,11,FConservative government in March 2022
OL,12,F` would be extended until the end of
OL,13,FAugust 2026, with rates then gradually
OL,14,Freturning to previous levels over the
OL,15,Fnext five years.
OL,17,FThe government estimates this will
OL,18,Fsave the average motorist over #120.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
